  "sections": {
    "Description": "The Alpha Scorpion resembles the creature it is named after, stinger included. Its goal is to restrict units' mobility with webbing, then attack them.",
    "Strategy": "Much like the standardScorpion, the Alpha Scorpion has high health but low mobility. Try to deploy your Mechs with weapons that can free themselves near it, or otherwise keep them away from the Alpha Scorpion's movement range so it instead targets an already stationary building or objective. The Alpha Scorpion is one of the sturdier enemies at 5 health, so it's recommended to use bump damage and displaced enemy attacks to wear it down."
  },
  "full_text": "Alpha Scorpion\nDetails\nHealth\n5\nMove\n3\nSystems\nGoring Spinneret\n(\nEnemy\n)\nEffect\nWeb an adjacent target, preparing to stab it for 3 damage.\nAlpha Scorpion\nis one of the Alpha\nVek\nfrom\nInto The Breach\n.\nDescription\n[\n]\nThe Alpha Scorpion resembles the creature it is named after, stinger included. Its goal is to restrict units' mobility with webbing, then attack them.\nStrategy\n[\n]\nMuch like the standard\nScorpion\n, the Alpha Scorpion has high health but low mobility. Try to deploy your Mechs with weapons that can free themselves near it, or otherwise keep them away from the Alpha Scorpion's movement range so it instead targets an already stationary building or objective. The Alpha Scorpion is one of the sturdier enemies at 5 health, so it's recommended to use bump damage and displaced enemy attacks to wear it down.\nv\n·\nd\n·\ne\nVek\nVek\nBeetle\n•\nBlobber\n•\nBurrower\n•\nCentipede\n•\nCrab\n•\nDigger\n•\nFirefly\n•\nHornet\n•\nLeaper\n•\nScarab\n•\nScorpion\n•\nSpider\n•\nVolatile Vek\nVek (Advanced Edition)\nBouncer\n•\nGastropod\n•\nMosquito\n•\nMoth\n•\nPlasmodia\n•\nStarfish\n•\nTumblebug\nAlpha Vek\nAlpha Beetle\n•\nAlpha Blobber\n•\nAlpha Burrower\n•\nAlpha Centipede\n•\nAlpha Crab\n•\nAlpha Digger\n•\nAlpha Firefly\n•\nAlpha Hornet\n•\nAlpha Leaper\n•\nAlpha Scarab\n•\nAlpha Scorpion\n•\nAlpha Spider\nAlpha Vek (Advanced Edition)\nAlpha Bouncer\n•\nAlpha Gastropod\n•\nAlpha Mosquito\n•\nAlpha Moth\n•\nAlpha Plasmodia\n•\nAlpha Starfish\n•\nAlpha Tumblebug\nVek Psions\nBlast Psion\n•\nBlood Psion\n•\nShell Psion\n•\nSoldier Psion\nVek Psions (Advanced Edition)\nArachnid Psion\n•\nRaging Psion\n•\nSmoldering Psion\nVek Minions\nBlob\n•\nAlpha Blob\n•\nSpiderling Egg\n•\nSpiderling\n•\nAlpha Spiderling\nVek Minions (Advanced Edition)\nSpore\n•\nAlpha Spore\n•\nVicious Spore\n•\nBlob Leader\nVek Leaders\nBeetle Leader\n•\nFirefly Leader\n•\nHornet Leader\n•\nLarge Goo\n(\nMedium Goo\n) (\nSmall Goo\n) •\nPsion Abomina